Subscribe to your favorite idols CoStar 
 channel to meet them live via video and get 
 exclusive access to behind-the-scenes 
 content, their inner sanctum and more.

Join FanCasts on CoStar to meet, hang out 
 and talk with your favorite idols live via video. 
 Just submit your questions to register so you 
 can take part and have fun.

Watch all FanCasts and behind-the-scenes 
 footage from your favorite idols via StarCast - 
 streamed live from location or view on 
 demand through CoStars video library.

Get the insiders view to learn more about your 
 favorite celebrities real life with CoStars 
 Insider Series monthly episodes, up-to-date
